{"type": "article", "id": 30568, "title": "Kate Spade股价暴跌，以及，阿迪正式发布 NMD_XR1 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-04T02:52:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 707, "name": "Margaret Howell"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 31065, "name": "NMD_XR1"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 6654, "name": "Etsy"}, {"id": 18457, "name": "Safilo"}, {"id": 31066, "name": "Steve Madden"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804104258cjLfUByz4sDOKNQm.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/etsy-earnings-10500620/\" rel=\"nofollow\">手工艺品电商 Etsy 第二季度收入飙升 39%</a> </b>| 在第二季度，Etsy 的全球社区又扩大了，包括约 170 万活跃卖家和 26.1 万个活跃的买家。Etsy 的 CEO  Chad Dickerson 表示，公司将加快实现销售总额的增长，为创意卖家提供高质量的服务。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/financial/shares-kate-spade-drop-q2-eps-miss-fashion-apparel-accessories-10500918/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Kate Spade 股价暴跌</b></a> | Kate Spade 在第二季度收入为 3.2 亿美元，平均每股收益为 11 美分，并未达到之前华尔街预期的 14 美分每股。CEO Craig A. Leavitt 表示，全球零售业格局的改变、持续的旅游低迷和太多打折产品使 Kate Spade 的第二季度业绩未能达到预期。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/trends/forum-for-bringing-the-fashion-and-tech-worlds-together-10500568/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>第三届时尚科技论坛将于 10 月 13 日于布鲁克林召开</b></a> | 论坛邀请了 Tesla, Google 和 Levi’s 等多家公司发言，将讨论如何把科技引入时尚。</p><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Steve-Madden-sales-climbs-slightly-adjusts-2016-sales-outlook,719635.html#.V6KIG2XcwU0\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Steve Madden 线上销售增长缓慢</b></a> | Steve Madden 第二季度的线上销售同比增长了 0.6%，CEO Edward Rosenfeld 表示，Steve Madden 女鞋和 Dolce Vita 的鞋类部门表现稳健，核心业务的增长超过了预期。 Steve Madden 调整了 2016 年线上销售预期至 1% 的同比增长率。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>MARGARET HOWELL 发布<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/margaret-howell-fall-2016-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2016 秋季新品</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608041041443XDyCcwQip74UAnM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.313643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804104153wqIctMex87WKQXRJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.278736\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804104204vD6xbl2CnfqpMcmN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.294707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>A Bathing Ape 打造<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/a-bathing-ape-unveils-an-air-yeezy-inspired-roadsta\" rel=\"nofollow\">全新 Roadster 配色</a>，它的夜光色鞋底有可能成为下一个热点。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804094857kFu8vifgCrWyl03E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804094906MagXsP4YBGbWO7xw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>adidas Originals 正式发布 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/adidas-originals-nmdxr1\" rel=\"nofollow\">NMD_XR1 鞋款</a>，升级之作更具流线型，将于 8 月 18 日登陆 adidas Originals 指定店铺。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608041008458ED90uryeIZhGbtQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804100856Oko12gGLpzNXla0b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.paul-joe-beaute.com/en/creation/16au/park.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paul Joe 发布秋冬新品</a>，以及和 Tom &amp; Jerry 